pageContext.claim: “The Supreme Court sends case back to Lower Court, arguments to continue. This is all a political prosecution. I won the Mueller Witch Hunt, and others, and now I have to keep fighting in a politically corrupt New York. Not fair to this Presidency or Administration!”
pageContext.analysis: This is a criminal investigation. The Manhattan DA had subpoenaed Trump's records as part of a criminal probe into potential wrongdoing by the president and his organization resulting from the guilty plea of former Trump fixer Michael Cohen -- a case brought by Trump's Justice Department.
